00:32:02.520 --> 00:32:06.260
How might you regulate?

00:32:06.260 --> 00:32:06.760
Max.

00:32:06.760 --> 00:32:08.153
AUDIENCE: Price floor.

00:32:08.153 --> 00:32:10.320
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: Well,
