Wireless, it surely is.

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:09.989
That's why we can have
competing wireless companies.

00:34:09.989 --> 00:34:11.590
We have maybe three in Europe.

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:12.960
They tend to have more.

00:34:12.960 --> 00:34:13.860
That's easy.

00:34:13.860 --> 00:34:17.500
But wireline, that's tough.

